- Above the main Headline ("Silence Isn't Gone"), add a small, uppercase label.
- Text: "THE NEURO-SOMATIC TINNITUS SOLUTION"
- Style: Font-size 0.8rem, Letter-spacing 3px, Color `--neuro-glow` (#00D4FF), Sans-Serif, Uppercase.
- This creates immediate context without changing the main poetic headline.

**2. UPGRADE THE ORB (Make it visible & structured):**
- Instead of a faint blur, create a **"Neural Halo"**.
