- Code logic:
  ```css
  .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%; /* Position behind text, slightly offset if needed */
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 50vw;
      height: 50vw;
      border-radius: 50%;
      /* Create a glowing ring */
